  <summary>4/14/1997--Introduced.
Counter-Narcotics Policy Review Act - Establishes the High Level Commission on International Narcotics Control to determine and report to the Congress on the effectiveness of the annual certification process relating to international narcotics control in curtailing international drug trafficking and in reducing drug use and consumption within the United States. Authorizes appropriations.</summary>
